properties.description: Built in the Georgian style, the Guildhall brought together Kingston's administrative functions. Purpose-built Magistrates Courts were included in the building, part of which are now home to Kingston History Centre.
properties.name: Kingston Guildhall and History Centre

properties.description:
A Victorian chocolate factory conversion with exposed girders, brickwork and Crittal-style windows. 

No 50 was transformed from a flat into a traditional, bespoke shoemaking workshop, showroom and shoe & leather craft training school.
properties.name: Carreducker at 50 Chocolate Studios
